<sect1 id="ch-system-udev" role="wrap" revision="sysv">
  <?dbhtml filename="udev.html"?>

  <sect1info condition="script">
<productname>udev</productname>
<productnumber>&systemd-version;</productnumber> <address>&systemd-url;</address></sect1info>

  <title>Systemd-&systemd-version; 의 Udev</title>

  <indexterm zone="ch-system-udev">
    <primary sortas="a-Udev">Udev</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title/>

    <para>Udev 패키지에는 장치 노드 동적 생성용 프로그램이 들어 있습니다.</para>

    <segmentedlist>
      <segtitle>&buildtime;</segtitle>
      <segtitle>&diskspace;</segtitle>

      <seglistitem>
        <seg>&udev-fin-sbu;</seg>
        <seg>&udev-fin-du;</seg>
      </seglistitem>
    </segmentedlist>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Udev 설치</title>

    <para>Udev는 systemd-&systemd-version; 패키지의 일부입니다. 소스 tarball로는
systemd-&systemd-version;.tar.xz 파일을 쓰십시오.</para>

    <para>Remove two unneeded groups, <systemitem
class="groupname">render</systemitem> and <systemitem
class="groupname">sgx</systemitem>, from the default udev rules:</para>

 <screen><userinput remap="pre">sed -e 's/GROUP="render"/GROUP="video"/' \
    -e 's/GROUP="sgx", //'               \
    -i rules.d/50-udev-default.rules.in</userinput></screen>

    <para>전체 Systemd 설치가 필요한 udev 규칙 하나를 제거:</para>

 <!-- Not needed in 258.1
    <para>
Fix a bug that prevents udev from running correctly:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="pre">sed -i "/udev_dependencies,/a \                'link_with': udev_link_with," src/udev/meson.build</userinput></screen>
-->
<screen><userinput remap="pre">sed -i '/systemd-sysctl/s/^/#/' rules.d/99-systemd.rules.in</userinput></screen>

    <para>독립형(standalone) udev 설치를 위해 하드코딩된 네트워크 설정 파일 경로들을 수정:</para>

 <screen><userinput remap="pre">sed -e '/NETWORK_DIRS/s/systemd/udev/' \
    -i src/libsystemd/sd-network/network-util.h</userinput></screen>

    <para>Udev 컴파일 준비하기:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="configure">mkdir -p build
cd       build

meson setup ..                  \
      --prefix=/usr             \
      --buildtype=release       \
      -D mode=release           \
      -D dev-kvm-mode=0660      \
      -D link-udev-shared=false \
      -D logind=false           \
      -D vconsole=false</userinput></screen>

    <variablelist>
      <title>The meaning of the meson options:</title>

      <varlistentry>
        <term><parameter>--buildtype=release</parameter></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>This switch overrides the default buildtype (<quote>debug</quote>), which
produces unoptimized binaries.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term><parameter>-D mode=release</parameter></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>Disable some features considered experimental by upstream.
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term><parameter>-D dev-kvm-mode=0660</parameter></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>The default udev rule would allow all users to access <filename
class='devicefile'>/dev/kvm</filename>.  The editors consider it dangerous.
This option overrides it.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term><parameter>-D link-udev-shared=false</parameter></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>This option prevents udev from linking to the internal systemd shared
library, <systemitem class='library'>libsystemd-shared</systemitem>.  This
library is designed to be shared by many Systemd components and it's too
overkill for a udev-only installation.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term><parameter>-D logind=false -D vconsole=false</parameter></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>These options prevent the generation of several udev rule files belonging to
the other Systemd components that we won't install.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para>제공된 udev helper 목록을 가져와 환경 변수에 저장합니다. (반드시 export할 필요는 없지만, 일반 사용자 권한으로
빌드하거나 패키지 관리자를 사용할 때 더 편리):</para>

    <screen><userinput remap="make">export udev_helpers=$(grep "'name' :" ../src/udev/meson.build | \
                      awk '{print $3}' | tr -d ",'" | grep -v 'udevadm')</userinput></screen>

    <para>udev에 필요한 구성 요소만 빌드:</para>

    <screen><userinput remap="make">ninja udevadm systemd-hwdb                                           \
      $(ninja -n | grep -Eo '(src/(lib)?udev|rules.d|hwdb.d)/[^ ]*') \
      $(realpath libudev.so --relative-to .)                         \
      $udev_helpers</userinput></screen>

    <para>패키지 설치:</para>

    <screen><userinput remap="install">install -vm755 -d {/usr/lib,/etc}/udev/{hwdb.d,rules.d,network}
install -vm755 -d /usr/{lib,share}/pkgconfig
install -vm755 udevadm                             /usr/bin/
install -vm755 systemd-hwdb                        /usr/bin/udev-hwdb
ln      -svfn  ../bin/udevadm                      /usr/sbin/udevd
cp      -av    libudev.so{,*[0-9]}                 /usr/lib/
install -vm644 ../src/libudev/libudev.h            /usr/include/
install -vm644 src/libudev/*.pc                    /usr/lib/pkgconfig/
install -vm644 src/udev/*.pc                       /usr/share/pkgconfig/
install -vm644 ../src/udev/udev.conf               /etc/udev/
install -vm644 rules.d/* ../rules.d/README         /usr/lib/udev/rules.d/
install -vm644 $(find ../rules.d/*.rules \
                      -not -name '*power-switch*') /usr/lib/udev/rules.d/
install -vm644 hwdb.d/*  ../hwdb.d/{*.hwdb,README} /usr/lib/udev/hwdb.d/
install -vm755 $udev_helpers                       /usr/lib/udev
install -vm644 ../network/99-default.link          /usr/lib/udev/network</userinput></screen>

    <para>LFS 환경에서 유용한 몇 가지 사용자 정의 규칙과 지원 파일들을 설치:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="install">tar -xvf ../../&udev-lfs-version;.tar.xz
make -f &udev-lfs-version;/Makefile.lfs install</userinput></screen>

    <para>맨 페이지 설치:</para>

    
<screen><!-- Please make sure systemd man pages tarball has a common leading
         component in the path.  -->
<userinput remap="install">tar -xf ../../systemd-man-pages-&systemd-man-version;.tar.xz                          \
    --no-same-owner --strip-components=1                              \
    -C /usr/share/man --wildcards '*/udev*' '*/libudev*'              \
                                  '*/systemd.link.5'                  \
                                  '*/systemd-'{hwdb,udevd.service}.8

sed 's|systemd/network|udev/network|'                                 \
    /usr/share/man/man5/systemd.link.5                                \
  > /usr/share/man/man5/udev.link.5

sed 's/systemd\(\\\?-\)/udev\1/' /usr/share/man/man8/systemd-hwdb.8   \
                               > /usr/share/man/man8/udev-hwdb.8

sed 's|lib.*udevd|sbin/udevd|'                                        \
    /usr/share/man/man8/systemd-udevd.service.8                       \
  > /usr/share/man/man8/udevd.8

rm /usr/share/man/man*/systemd*</userinput></screen>

    <para>마지막으로, <envar>udev_helpers</envar> 변수의 설정을 해제:</para>

    
    <screen><!-- remap="make" seems confusing but we don't have sth. like
         remap="clean".  -->
<userinput remap="install">unset udev_helpers</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 id="conf-udev" role="configuration">
    <title>Configuring Udev</title>

    <indexterm zone="conf-udev">
      <primary sortas="a-Udev">Udev</primary>
      <secondary>configuring</secondary>
    </indexterm>

    <indexterm zone="conf-udev">
      <primary sortas="e-/etc/udev/hwdb.bin">/etc/udev/hwdb.bin</primary>
    </indexterm>

    <para>하드웨어 장치 정보는 <filename class="directory">/etc/udev/hwdb.d</filename> 및
<filename class="directory">/usr/lib/udev/hwdb.d</filename> 디렉터리에서
관리됩니다. <application>Udev</application>가 이 정보를 쓰려면
<filename>/etc/udev/hwdb.bin</filename> 바이너리 데이터베이스로 컴파일해야 합니다. 다음 명령으로 초기
데이터베이스를 생성:</para>

<screen><userinput>udev-hwdb update</userinput></screen>

    <para>이 명령은 하드웨어 정보가 업데이트될 때마다 실행해야 합니다.</para>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 id="contents-udev" role="content">
    <title>Udev 구성 요소</title>

    <segmentedlist>
      <segtitle>설치된 프로그램</segtitle>
      <segtitle>Installed libraries</segtitle>
      <segtitle>설치된 디렉터리</segtitle>

      <seglistitem>
        <seg>udevadm, udevd (symlink to udevadm), 및 udev-hwdb</seg>

        <seg>libudev.so</seg>

        <seg>/etc/udev 및 /usr/lib/udev</seg>
      </seglistitem>
    </segmentedlist>

    <variablelist>
      <bridgehead renderas="sect3">짧은 설명</bridgehead>
      <?dbfo list-presentation="list"?> <?dbhtml list-presentation="table"?>
      <varlistentry id="udevadm" revision="sysv">
        <term><command>udevadm</command></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>일반 udev 관리 도구: udevd 데몬을 제어하고, Udev 데이터베이스로부터 정보를 제공하며, uevent를 모니터링하고,
uevent가 끝날 때까지 기다리며, Udev 설정을 테스트하고, 지정된 장치에 대한 uevent를 발생</para>
          <indexterm zone="ch-system-udev udevadm">
            <primary sortas="b-udevadm">udevadm</primary>
          </indexterm>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry id="udevd">
        <term><command>udevd</command></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>넷링크(netlink) 소켓에서 uevent를 리스닝(listening)하고, 장치를 생성하며, 이러한 uevent에 대응하여 설정된
외부 프로그램들을 실행하는 데몬</para>
          <indexterm zone="ch-system-udev udevd">
            <primary sortas="b-udevd">udevd</primary>
          </indexterm>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry id="udev-hwdb">
        <term><command>udev-hwdb</command></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>하드웨어 데이터베이스를 업데이트 또는 쿼리.</para>
          <indexterm zone="ch-system-udev udev-hwdb">
            <primary sortas="b-udev-hwdb">udev-hwdb</primary>
          </indexterm>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry id="libudev">
        <term><filename class="libraryfile">libudev</filename></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>udev 장치 정보에 접근하기 위한 라이브러리 인터페이스</para>
          <indexterm zone="ch-system-udev libudev">
            <primary sortas="c-libudev">libudev</primary>
          </indexterm>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry id="etc-udev">
        <term><filename class="directory">/etc/udev</filename></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>Udev 설정 파일, 장치 권한, 그리고 장치 명명(naming) 규칙을 포함</para>
          <indexterm zone="ch-system-udev etc-udev">
            <primary sortas="e-/etc/udev">/etc/udev</primary>
          </indexterm>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

    </variablelist>

  </sect2>

</sect1>
